ng the existence of a\nlower bound for the spectrum of the Schr\\\"{o}dinger operator $-\\Delta -\\mu V$.\nIn the context of both interior and boundary singularities we show that the\ncritical constants in the weak Hardy inequality are $(N-2)^2/(4n-4)$ and\n$N^2/(4n-4)$, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2014 20:13:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Mar 2014 15:10:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 28 Sep 2014 17:31:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2015 06:29:56 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 11 Jul 2015 08:28:35 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sun, 22 Nov 2015 10:51:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-24"}
