 field section. This also sheds some\nlight on the possibility to effectivize constructions of integer parts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2014 11:07:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2016 13:40:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-14"}
